#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn2.13"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.13:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.13:0.2"
msgid "2. Anāthapiṇḍikavagga "
msgstr "2. With Anāthapiṇḍika "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.13:0.3"
msgid "13. Dīghalaṭṭhisutta "
msgstr "13. With Dīghalaṭṭhi "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn2.13:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "sn2.13:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the squirrels’ feeding ground. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.13:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho dīghalaṭṭhi devaputto abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ veḷuvanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. "
msgstr "Then, late at night, the glorious god Dīghalaṭṭhi, lighting up the entire Bamboo Grove, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side, "

msgctxt "sn2.13:1.4"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho dīghalaṭṭhi devaputto bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "and recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.120, sc2
msgctxt "sn2.13:2.1"
msgid "“Bhikkhu siyā jhāyī vimuttacitto, "
msgstr "“Suppose a mendicant is a meditator, freed in mind. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.13:2.2"
msgid "Ākaṅkhe ce hadayassānupattiṃ; "
msgstr "If they want to reach the heart’s peace, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.13:2.3"
msgid "Lokassa ñatvā udayabbayañca, "
msgstr "having known the arising and passing of the world, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.13:2.4"
msgid "Sucetaso anissito tadānisaṃso”ti. "
msgstr "healthy-minded, independent, that is their reward.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
